                                  <div id="collapseTextE1" class="panel-collapse collapse">
                                      <div class="panel-body">
                                        In the early days of Bitcoin, anyone could find a new block using their computer's CPU. As more and more people started mining, the difficulty of finding new blocks increased greatly to the point where the only cost-effective method of mining today is using specialized hardware. You can visit <a href="http://www.BitcoinMining.com">BitcoinMining.com</a> for more information.
