                                <div class="panel panel-default">
                                    <div class="panel-heading">
                                      <h4 class="panel-title">
                                          <a class="accordion-toggle" data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordionTextE" href="#collapseTextE2">b) How Can I Buy Bitcoin via a Credit Card or Paypal ?</a>
                                      </h4>
                                  </div>
                                  <div id="collapseTextE2" class="panel-collapse collapse">
                                      <div class="panel-body">
                                        It is not advisable to buy Bitcoin with either a credit card or Paypal. All forms of these types of payments are excluded to eliminate fraud (by doing a fraudulent charge-back). For this reason, none of the big exchanges accept these as forms of payment.
                                        <br/>
                                        <br/>
                                        In short, you cannot (directly) use these to buy bitcoins at exchanges.
